WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:17.273 --> 00:00:22.113
 This is a Saber Strike 2014 exercise 

00:00:22.113 --> 00:00:27.473
 [Captain James Walton] This is the third time that international partners are practicing together. 

00:00:27.473 --> 00:00:32.833
 This year, over 4,000 soldiers from over ten countries will participate in the exercise. 

00:00:33.240 --> 00:00:43.836
 Different countries can work together on diverse collaborations with different performance, 

00:00:43.836 --> 00:00:48.116
 where we can improve our interoperability. 

00:00:48.140 --> 00:00:51.957
 This is an important exercise for all our international partners 

00:00:51.957 --> 00:00:55.857
 In the Baltic and European region 

00:00:55.857 --> 00:01:00.997
 because it gives us the opportunity to strengthen our cooperation 

00:01:01.000 --> 00:01:08.480
 practicing together in field conditions and staff level. 

00:01:10.840 --> 00:01:13.580
 The exercise consists of three different exercises: 

00:01:13.620 --> 00:01:18.500
