 Finland participates in head coaching 

00:01:23.280 --> 00:01:27.660
 as part of the battalion's staff. 

00:01:27.660 --> 00:01:36.400
 The Department is also supported by the Finnish International Standby Force Communications and Headquarters unit. 

00:01:36.400 --> 00:01:47.220
 Exercise improves operational capability of participating troops, battalion staff, and messaging and staffing 

00:01:47.220 --> 00:01:52.100
 but also with other forces. 

00:01:52.100 --> 00:02:00.140
 For staff working with senior staffs and adjacent forces 

00:02:00.140 --> 00:02:16.460
 Commanders and messengers for operation and practice with foreign soldiers. 

00:02:17.320 --> 00:02:27.020
 An individual warrior gets experience working with foreign soldiers 

00:02:27.020 --> 00:02:35.700
 This experience will benefit them if they participate in international operations in the future. 

00:02:37.780 --> 00:02:44.280
 In addition to working with a Finnish mechanized icebreaker battalion 

00:02:44.280 --> 00:02:49.200
